The mega strike forces gather
The unions of the League and the National Association of Labour Councils will constitute their strike commission, which will be responsible for coordinating the indeterminate strike on Monday.
A general protest meeting will be held on Saturday and Monday, on the day of the final vote on the Health Cash Act, the strike will begin.
This action will certainly cause significant stoppers in traffic because rail traffic will be almost completely stopped and BKV employees will also strike up to 13:00 a.m.
The League Syndicates will announce on Friday afternoon the details of their Monday strike, organized with the National Association of Workers’ Counsel.
The LIGA - MOSZ strike committee will also be formed, it will serve as coordinator of Monday’s actions.
